descriptionHtml:
I just lost my hard drive, it died, so when i reloaded all my details onto the new drive, I was a little annoyed that I had to start again. Then i found two of my old files on a USB, so i thought I'd upload them on here in case it happens again. The first file is my character Missy at level one, inside Helgen, the second file is where i just finished the Main Quest only. No Cheats

Files I use to make her pretty
DIMONIZED UNP female bodyby dimon99     http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6709
The Eyes Of Beautyby Gabriel Mailhot        http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/13722
Women of Skyrim-Enhanced female normalmapsby zzjay    http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/20483
Women of Skyrim female face texture and COMPANIONSby zzjay  http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/25588
Children of Skyrim - New Nord Presets and MORE - by FastestDog - FULLY SEVENBASE UNPB CBBE ECE CHARGEN COMPATIBLEby FastestDogInTheDistrict
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/21184
Hairs by SG Hairs, google it pleae
You will need Race Menu, http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/29624
Char Gen http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/36925
A new plugin for SKSE - Show Race Menu Precache Killer by Kapaer http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/33526
Skyrim Script Extender (SKSE) http://skse.silverlock.org/
and I have Dragonborn, Hearthfire, Dawnguard.


I would like to thank all the mod authors for without them, my girl would probably look like a draugr.
author: Unspacey
